1
00:00:03,460 --> 00:00:06,420
=Tolong, Jangan Manjakan Aku=
=Episode 10=

2
00:00:08,930 --> 00:00:09,490
Kak,

3
00:00:09,820 --> 00:00:10,320
bagaimana?

4
00:00:10,730 --> 00:00:11,420
Di luar sini,

5
00:00:11,610 --> 00:00:12,750
jauh lebih ramai daripada
istanamu, 'kan?

6
00:00:14,010 --> 00:00:14,870
Memang lumayan.

7
00:00:15,350 --> 00:00:15,700
Kak,

8
00:00:16,310 --> 00:00:17,100
apa kau mau makan Tanghulu?

9
00:00:18,050 --> 00:00:19,360
Boleh, belikan satu tusuk.

10
00:00:19,570 --> 00:00:20,020
Tunggu, ya.

11
00:00:27,690 --> 00:00:28,100
Kak.

12
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:30,610
Bagaimana kalau kau jangan
kembali ke istana dulu?

13
00:00:31,010 --> 00:00:33,010
Jika kau selalu ada di rumah seperti ini,

14
00:00:33,010 --> 00:00:34,130
kau bisa terus menemaniku bermain.

15
00:00:34,130 --> 00:00:34,960
Sudah berapa usiamu?

16
00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:36,380
Masih mau Kakak menemanimu bermain?

17
00:00:38,690 --> 00:00:39,730
(Namun...)

18
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:41,920
(jika bukan karena tugas 100 hari
di Istana Pengasingan,)

19
00:00:42,210 --> 00:00:44,900
(sebenarnya tinggal di luar memang
lebih enak daripada di istana.)

20
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:48,230
(Namun, jika aku tidak segera kembali
ke Istana Pengasingan,)

21
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:50,280
(entah kapan lagi
aku akan dibunuh.)

22
00:00:51,230 --> 00:00:51,620
(Tidak bisa.)

23
00:00:52,230 --> 00:00:53,460
(Aku harus memikirkan cara lagi.)

24
00:00:54,720 --> 00:00:55,100
Kak?

25
00:00:56,290 --> 00:00:56,620
Tidak apa.

26
00:00:57,660 --> 00:00:58,100
Ayo,

27
00:00:58,100 --> 00:00:59,190
Kakak bawa kau pergi makan.

28
00:00:59,400 --> 00:00:59,790
Ayo.

29
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:00,100
Baik.

30
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:03,220
(Kedai Zuixiao)

31
00:01:03,220 --> 00:01:04,690
Ke depannya,
jangan sering membuat masalah lagi.

32
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:07,680
Lalu, lebih sering berbuat baik
saja sudah cukup.

33
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:08,080
Dengar, tidak?

34
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:11,500
Berbuat baik?

35
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,720
Aku pandai membuat masalah,

36
00:01:15,090 --> 00:01:17,630
jika berbuat baik, bukankah aku
tidak berpengalaman?

37
00:01:18,700 --> 00:01:20,940
Berbuat baik perlu pengalaman apa?

38
00:01:21,140 --> 00:01:22,260
Bantulah orang untuk merasa senang.

39
00:01:22,790 --> 00:01:25,300
Bantu orang untuk merasa senang?

40
00:01:27,290 --> 00:01:27,940
Keluar, keluar!

41
00:01:28,500 --> 00:01:29,770
Pergi sana, keluar!

42
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:30,560
Kau kurang ajar sekali!

43
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,030
Sana, sana!

44
00:01:31,410 --> 00:01:32,450
Tidak punya uang, mau minum apa?

45
00:01:33,970 --> 00:01:34,620
Kuajarkan padamu, ya.

46
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:35,340
Lihat baik-baik.

47
00:01:35,970 --> 00:01:37,240
Pak Tua, mari duduk di sini.

48
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,120
Duduklah bersama kami.

49
00:01:41,220 --> 00:01:41,670
Aku?

50
00:01:41,670 --> 00:01:41,970
Ya.

51
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:42,890
Sini, sini, sini.

52
00:01:44,020 --> 00:01:44,760
Kau duduk di sana.

53
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,230
Sana.

54
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:45,640
Geser.

55
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:49,080
Nona,

56
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,770
Anda sungguh murah hati.

57
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,150
Pelayan toko itu,

58
00:01:52,340 --> 00:01:53,820
sungguh tidak bisa menilai orang.

59
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,650
Dia menganggapku pengemis,

60
00:01:55,650 --> 00:01:56,540
dan ingin mengusirku pergi.

61
00:01:56,540 --> 00:01:57,340
Menyebalkan, 'kan?

62
00:01:58,830 --> 00:01:59,270
Pak Tua.

63
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:00,880
Bukankah kau memang pengemis?

64
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,220
Mana tata krama bicaramu?

65
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:04,880
Jangan hiraukan dia.

66
00:02:04,880 --> 00:02:05,560
Mari, minum.

67
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:06,270
Minumlah.

68
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:14,720
Apa boleh tambah segelas lagi?

69
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,880
Boleh, boleh, boleh.

70
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:22,570
Jarang sekali ada gadis yang menjamuku
dengan begitu ramah.

71
00:02:23,220 --> 00:02:24,000
Arak ini,

72
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:26,060
aku tidak bisa minum begitu saja.

73
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,250
Kita bisa bertemu karena takdir.

74
00:02:32,340 --> 00:02:32,680
Mari,

75
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,520
kita minum lagi.

76
00:02:35,170 --> 00:02:35,750
Minum segelas lagi.

77
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:46,980
Pak Tua,

78
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:48,580
kau sudah mabuk, ya?

79
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:49,580
Lagi...

80
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:51,810
lagi... lagi...

81
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:55,780
Memalukan sekali.

82
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:59,490
Namun, tanda pengenal ini
lumayan bagus juga.

83
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,270
Ini barang orang, kembalikan padanya.

84
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:03,580
Xue Daoyuan?

85
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:06,020
Sebentar.

86
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,280
Xue Daoyuan?

87
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:17,060
Karakter Xue Daoyuan.

88
00:03:17,100 --> 00:03:17,940
(Xue Daoyuan)

89
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:24,020
orang pintar yang terkenal,

90
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:27,220
paling ahli dalam ilmu kedokteran.

91
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:31,050
Hobi terbesar dalam hidupnya adalah

92
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:32,660
minum arak.

93
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:33,300
(Xue Daoyuan)

94
00:03:34,490 --> 00:03:36,100
Ini adalah Xue Daoyuan?

95
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:38,410
Kak, kau mengenalnya?

96
00:03:38,930 --> 00:03:40,830
Aku sangat mengenalnya.

97
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,970
(Dia adalah karakter penting
dalam novelku.)

98
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:49,600
(Di novel, dia akan datang ke ibu kota
pada tanggal 6 Juni.)

99
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,190
(Kebetulan juga merupakan hari ini.)

100
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:54,060
(Dia bertemu Qin Yu yang terkena
racun kuat.)

101
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:56,400
(Tanggal 6 Juni)
Di dalam novel, pada tanggal 6 Juni,

102
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,270
karakter utama pria kita, Qin Yu,

103
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,460
menghadapi sebuah masa kritis
yang besar dalam hidupnya,

104
00:04:01,740 --> 00:04:03,520
terkena racun berbahaya,

105
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,270
hidupnya dalam bahaya.

106
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,260
Saat Qin Yu melarikan diri,

107
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:10,430
dia bertemu Xue Daoyuan, Tabib Xue,

108
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:13,040
dan berhasil selamat tanpa masalah,

109
00:04:13,230 --> 00:04:17,140
dia bahkan jatuh cinta kepada
murid wanita Xue Daoyuan,

110
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,380
pulang membawa seorang wanita cantik.

111
00:04:20,580 --> 00:04:21,240
Gawat, gawat.

112
00:04:22,250 --> 00:04:24,730
Qin si Licik ini akan mati
gara-gara aku sendiri.

113
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:26,630
Xue.

114
00:04:27,470 --> 00:04:27,990
Xue!

115
00:04:28,330 --> 00:04:29,450
Kau tidak boleh mabuk begini!

116
00:04:29,450 --> 00:04:30,910
Kau masih memiliki tugas yang sangat penting!

117
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:32,560
Xue! Xue!

118
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:36,150
Begini saja,

119
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:38,640
kau bawa dia ke sebuah gubuk di
gunung bagian barat kota.

120
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,570
Di sana adalah tempat tinggalnya.

121
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,900
Kak, bagaimana kau bisa tahu
tempat tinggalnya?

122
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,240
Kau jangan banyak tanya!

123
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,440
Aku yang tulis, tentu saja aku tahu!

124
00:04:46,570 --> 00:04:48,180
Tugasmu adalah membangunkan dia.

125
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:50,170
Aku akan mencarimu satu jam lagi.

126
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:52,480
Kak, kau mau pergi ke mana?

127
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,140
Memadamkan api!

128
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,100
Baginda.

129
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,350
Ini digambar olehku secara diam-diam.

130
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:02,880
Formasi prajurit di barisan depan Xirong,

131
00:05:03,180 --> 00:05:04,740
situasi kekuatan utama prajurit Xirong,

132
00:05:04,810 --> 00:05:06,940
lokasi markas dan gudang
penyimpanan makanan.

133
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:07,730
Semuanya ada di sana.

134
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:50,420
Cepat pergi!

135
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:00,320
Pak Tua,

136
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,200
bangunlah.

137
00:06:03,090 --> 00:06:03,450
Pak Tua!

